{
  "video_id": "0H6j5-6DtXw",
  "title": "What if I'm busted for \"resisting arrest\" in Las Vegas, Nevada?",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 220.0,
      "end_time": 2455.0,
      "text": "-I&#39;m here today with top Las Vegas criminal defense"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2455.0,
      "end_time": 4080.0,
      "text": "lawyer, Michael Becker."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 4080.0,
      "end_time": 6580.0,
      "text": "And Mike, today I want to ask you"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 6580.0,
      "end_time": 9960.0,
      "text": "about the Nevada crime of resisting arrest."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 9960.0,
      "end_time": 13140.0,
      "text": "And the term resisting arrest is kind"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 13140.0,
      "end_time": 15010.0,
      "text": "of a buzz word in our culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 15010.0,
      "end_time": 18690.0,
      "text": "And I think most people think of it in the context of,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 18690.0,
      "end_time": 21640.0,
      "text": "the cops are trying to arrest you and you struggle."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 21640.0,
      "end_time": 24390.0,
      "text": "And you try to keep from being handcuffed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 24390.0,
      "end_time": 25820.0,
      "text": "or fight with the police."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 25820.0,
      "end_time": 27720.0,
      "text": "But actually, the law here in Nevada"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 27720.0,
      "end_time": 28900.0,
      "text": "is even broader than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 28900.0,
      "end_time": 30124.0,
      "text": "Is that right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 30124.0,
      "end_time": 30790.0,
      "text": "-That&#39;s correct."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 30790.0,
      "end_time": 34370.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s willfully resisting or obstructing law enforcement."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 34370.0,
      "end_time": 36290.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;ve seen people that were charged"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 36290.0,
      "end_time": 38960.0,
      "text": "under this provision of the NRS statutes."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 38960.0,
      "end_time": 44310.0,
      "text": "For example, pulling their hand away when the officer went"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 44310.0,
      "end_time": 48110.0,
      "text": "to put handcuffs on them, or the officer asked them their name"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 48110.0,
      "end_time": 49890.0,
      "text": "and they gave a false name."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 49890.0,
      "end_time": 53570.0,
      "text": "That could be the basis for a charge of willfully obstructing"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 53570.0,
      "end_time": 55750.0,
      "text": "or resisting law enforcement."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 55750.0,
      "end_time": 60710.0,
      "text": "-And certainly, if you struggle with the officer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 60710.0,
      "end_time": 63770.0,
      "text": "or if you get in a fight with a police officer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 63770.0,
      "end_time": 66610.0,
      "text": "then that could be resisting arrest or something even more"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 66610.0,
      "end_time": 67470.0,
      "text": "serious."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 67470.0,
      "end_time": 68210.0,
      "text": "-That&#39;s correct."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 68210.0,
      "end_time": 71110.0,
      "text": "I mean, if you run away from the police"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 71110.0,
      "end_time": 74750.0,
      "text": "or resist them in matters that we&#39;ve spoken of previously,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 74750.0,
      "end_time": 77080.0,
      "text": "that would likely lead to a misdemeanor charge"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 77080.0,
      "end_time": 79830.0,
      "text": "for willfully resisting or obstructing."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 79830.0,
      "end_time": 82560.0,
      "text": "But if you threaten a police officer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 82560.0,
      "end_time": 84440.0,
      "text": "or if you strike a police officer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 84440.0,
      "end_time": 87860.0,
      "text": "there are more serious charges, including battery on a police"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 87860.0,
      "end_time": 90530.0,
      "text": "officer, which could be a felony if injury occurs."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 90530.0,
      "end_time": 92310.0,
      "text": "-And that potentially could send someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 92310.0,
      "end_time": 94250.0,
      "text": "to prison for a number of years."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 94250.0,
      "end_time": 95600.0,
      "text": "-That&#39;s correct."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 95600.0,
      "end_time": 98130.0,
      "text": "-Have you had success in defending clients"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 98130.0,
      "end_time": 101190.0,
      "text": "over the years who are charged with resisting arrest?"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 101190.0,
      "end_time": 101690.0,
      "text": "-Yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 101690.0,
      "end_time": 103920.0,
      "text": "If often depends on the circumstances"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 103920.0,
      "end_time": 107280.0,
      "text": "that led to the contact with law enforcement."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 107280.0,
      "end_time": 110280.0,
      "text": "But more often than not, if you can"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 110280.0,
      "end_time": 112630.0,
      "text": "show that the defendant is not guilty"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 112630.0,
      "end_time": 116300.0,
      "text": "of the underlying conduct that gave rise to the charge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 116300.0,
      "end_time": 118270.0,
      "text": "a prosecutor and/or a court will be"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 118270.0,
      "end_time": 121290.0,
      "text": "a lot more likely to consider dismissing"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 121290.0,
      "end_time": 124820.0,
      "text": "the charge of resisting or obstructing arrest."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 124820.0,
      "end_time": 128330.0,
      "text": "-And what if it&#39;s a cop that-- let&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 128330.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131460.0,
      "text": "say you have a client who contacts you and the officer is"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 131460.0,
      "end_time": 134570.0,
      "text": "just exaggerating, or the officer"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 134570.0,
      "end_time": 138010.0,
      "text": "was brutal with the client."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 138010.0,
      "end_time": 141650.0,
      "text": "And we see that a lot here in Nevada."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 141650.0,
      "end_time": 144450.0,
      "text": "Are there things that you could do to sort of investigate"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 144450.0,
      "end_time": 148330.0,
      "text": "the police officer&#39;s background and kind of help bolster"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 148330.0,
      "end_time": 152930.0,
      "text": "our client&#39;s story as opposed to the police officer&#39;s?"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 152930.0,
      "end_time": 154020.0,
      "text": "-There are."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 154020.0,
      "end_time": 156820.0,
      "text": "We can, if we have a situation where the client says"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 156820.0,
      "end_time": 158710.0,
      "text": "that the officer was being overly"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 158710.0,
      "end_time": 162610.0,
      "text": "aggressive or inappropriate or using unnecessary force,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 162610.0,
      "end_time": 164860.0,
      "text": "placing the handcuffs on too tightly"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 164860.0,
      "end_time": 167030.0,
      "text": "or pulling the arm back too abruptly."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 167030.0,
      "end_time": 168280.0,
      "text": "-Which is very common, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 168280.0,
      "end_time": 169250.0,
      "text": "-It is common."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 169250.0,
      "end_time": 173610.0,
      "text": "And we can do a motion to look into the personnel records"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 173610.0,
      "end_time": 176560.0,
      "text": "of a police officer and determine"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 176560.0,
      "end_time": 179260.0,
      "text": "whether similar types of accusations"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 179260.0,
      "end_time": 181970.0,
      "text": "have been made against the officer in the past."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 181970.0,
      "end_time": 185660.0,
      "text": "And if we can show a prosecutor and/or a judge that we&#39;re"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 185660.0,
      "end_time": 188010.0,
      "text": "dealing with a situation where the officer may have"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 188010.0,
      "end_time": 190140.0,
      "text": "a history of being very aggressive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 190140.0,
      "end_time": 193250.0,
      "text": "then they&#39;re going to be a lot more receptive to our argument"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 193250.0,
      "end_time": 196770.0,
      "text": "that our client wasn&#39;t resisting, but was merely"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 196770.0,
      "end_time": 199810.0,
      "text": "rightfully protecting their personal sanctity."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 199810.0,
      "end_time": 203070.0,
      "text": "-So the take-home message to our audience"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 203070.0,
      "end_time": 206300.0,
      "text": "would be if you&#39;re charged with resisting arrest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 206300.0,
      "end_time": 209020.0,
      "text": "or battery on a police officer, something"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 209020.0,
      "end_time": 213980.0,
      "text": "similar, it&#39;s often in your interest to get a good lawyer"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 213980.0,
      "end_time": 216650.0,
      "text": "and to fight back, because it may be possible to get"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 216650.0,
      "end_time": 219110.0,
      "text": "the charges reduced or ultimately dismissed."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 219110.0,
      "end_time": 219830.0,
      "text": "-That&#39;s correct."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 219830.0,
      "end_time": 223390.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t believe that a normally law-abiding person"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 223390.0,
      "end_time": 227180.0,
      "text": "is going to be predisposed to resisting law enforcement."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 227180.0,
      "end_time": 229450.0,
      "text": "For the most part, we respect law enforcement"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 229450.0,
      "end_time": 231090.0,
      "text": "and we do what they tell us to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 231090.0,
      "end_time": 233746.0,
      "text": "Often, there&#39;s a story behind the story."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 233746.0,
      "end_time": 235370.0,
      "text": "So we like to sit down with our clients"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 235370.0,
      "end_time": 238620.0,
      "text": "and hear their side of the event so that we can go into court"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 238620.0,
      "end_time": 240900.0,
      "text": "and fight for an acquittal or a dismissal"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 240900.0,
      "end_time": 242270.0,
      "text": "of those types of charges."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 242270.0,
      "end_time": 245280.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m attorney Michael Becker with the Las Vegas Defense Group."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 245280.0,
      "end_time": 247660.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;ve been charged here in Nevada with resisting"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 247660.0,
      "end_time": 250690.0,
      "text": "an arrest, call me 702-DEFENSE, and we&#39;ll"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 250690.0,
      "end_time": 253750.0,
      "text": "talk about what we can do to get your charges reduced"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 253750.0,
      "end_time": 263750.0,
      "text": "or dismissed."
    }
  ]
